text = "The Fisher and Hunter each have randomly assigned “wanted”, “dud”, and “off-limits” fish.
- Wanted fish earn 200 points.
- Dud fish earn no points.
- Off-limits fish lose 100 points.
- Any other fish earns 100 points."
