text = "Move the fishing hook left and right using “A” and “D” respectively.
Press “S” to drop the hook down until it touches a fish, a coin, or the ground.
Press and hold “W” to make the hook go up faster.
Earn 200 points by hooking each of the five coins on the ground!
You can also use the respective arrow keys to control the hook."
autowrap_mode = 2

