text = "Use your mouse to aim your gun. Because you’re underwater, your crosshair is quite shaky: aim wisely!
Left click to shoot, preferably at the fish. There will be a short 1.25 seconds delay before the shot is fired.
You have 3 ammo bullets. You automatically reload upon running out of ammo. This takes 1.5 seconds."
autowrap_mode = 2

